==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tableware
<hw>Ta"ble*ware`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Ware, or articles
collectively, for use during meals, including, for example,
<examp>dishes</examp>, <examp>plates</examp>, <examp>bowls</examp>,
<examp>knives</examp>, <examp>forks</examp>, and
<examp>spoons</examp>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Table work</ent>⟦br⟧
